Podcast Description This week, Crouchy, Chris and Sids sit down with Dorking Wanderers manager and the viral sensation that is Marc White!
Marc lifts the lid on his humble, grassroots beginnings and the issues he faced when he decided to take on the role of manager after a rather boozy conversation down the pub.&nbsp;
We hear about Dorking’s meteoric rise from the lowest league of non-league football to the top of the non-league pyramid after receiving promotions every 2 years!

